{"tid":419922,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果時光倒流重新黎過 六合彩攪珠嘅結果會唔會完全一樣?","createTime":"2017-10-01T02:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T15:46:54.000Z","uid":137768,"like":13,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f427dd7ece39325874f54095c64f3d5870144937","tid":419922,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:49:18.000Z","msg":"用六合彩做例子 假設時光倒流重新黎過 六合彩攪珠嘅結果會唔會一模一樣?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會一樣 時光倒流姐係重播 再黎幾多次都係一樣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔一樣 隨機會有時間影響唔到嘅因素存在 或者影響左其他因素就算重新黎過 唔保證次次結果一樣<br />\n<br />\n其實可以有其他原因 亦唔一定只限於6合彩做例子 歡迎大家討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889d38c0a13336b26b2cdcb0eb4a0fecf8902f1e","tid":419922,"uid":38820,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:00:30.000Z","msg":"未試過答你唔到"},{"pid":"08874f4ce1ccae19697610ea077db7b814eaca69","tid":419922,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未試過答你唔到</blockquote><br />\n大家想像吓姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以隨便討論"},{"pid":"58076cabc3443d62d97517509b6b67d8a134f83d","tid":419922,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:53:54.000Z","msg":"又例如好多戲時光倒流會有唔同結果<br />\n係因為個主角保留之前嘅記憶<br />\n做唔同嘅決定<br />\n但如果佢無保留到呢<br />\n仲會唔會做出唔同嘅決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b138022aebb679a0734053de444089d9acd1b2","tid":419922,"uid":125152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:03:07.000Z","msg":"如果時間倒流，你嘅細胞都會倒流，所以你都唔會記得開左咩number<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc6cf6b13a7a26309b7cbdb18e506b23a88b0fa","tid":419922,"uid":36429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又例如好多戲時光倒流會有唔同結果<br />\n係因為